Class EdgeAL<D>

java.lang.Object
datastructure.graph.EdgeAL<D>
Type Parameters:
D - type of the data object
All Implemented Interfaces:
Edge<D>
public class EdgeAL<D> extends Object implements Edge<D>
Implementation of the edges of a generic Graph data structure composed of vertexes of type VertexAL containing data objects and implemented using Adjacent Lists. An edge contains a source vertex, a destination vertex and possibly a weight (the default weight is 0)
